snippet.textDisplay:
Salute from Hindustan to all respected Pakistan Singers especially to Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan Saab Ji, Reshma Ji, Abida Parveen Ji, Bohemia, Atif Aslam, QB, Umair Jaswal, Waqar, Sufi Sparrows, Pav Dharia & Khan Saab. Khan Saab I am deliberately waiting for new song like RIM JHIM. Atif Sir one thing in your songs is special & that is 'whenever I listen your songs in Coke Studio I always feels to talk to that supreme power (Allah Ji, Rabb Ji Baba Ji) & also wants to call my Parents because maa or papa hi sabse pehle aate hain bhagwan ke baad. Thanks from depth of my heart to give us beautiful songs.

Love you all.

Rabb Raakha
